Lazy Boy Game - Privacy Policy
Click here to check out our games
Effective Date:
August 2024
At Lazy Boy Games, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled responsibly. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you play our games.
1. Information We Do Not Collect
Lazy Boy Games does not collect or store any personally identifiable information (PII) from players of our games. We do not require you to provide any personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number to access or play our games.
2. No Tracking
We do not employ any tracking technologies or analytics services that would collect data about your gameplay or usage. Our games are designed to provide a fun and engaging experience without compromising your privacy.
3. Cookies and Similar Technologies
Lazy Boy Games does not use cookies or similar technologies to collect information from users. Our games operate without the need for any form of data tracking, ensuring that your privacy is maintained.
4. Data Security
While we do not collect personal data, we are committed to ensuring the security of any data we may inadvertently receive. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect any information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
5. Third-Party Services
Our games may contain links to third-party websites or services that may have different privacy practices. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party services you access. Lazy Boy Games is not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party services.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
Lazy Boy Games reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated policy. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:
